Package locals

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Localizable
    EN Localizable interface used in localizable objects such as locations and vehicles.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistributionCenter
    EN The Distribution Center is a Local derived class, used for harboring the warehouse and pickUp and drop-off locals, and vehicles in form of lists.
    DropOffLocal
    EN The DropOffLocal is a Local derived class, used for setting a drop-off local for the distribution center.
    Local
    EN The Local class is an abstract class referring to a location in the distribution center space used for identification of a physical space.
    PickUpLocal
    EN The PickUpLocal is a Local derived class, used for setting a pickup local for the distribution center.
    StorageLocal
    EN The StorageLocal is a Local derived class, used for setting a shelf local for the warehouse.
    Warehouse
    EN The Warehouse class is a Local derived class, used for harboring the storage locals in a form of a list.
